videos.description: Markieff Morris is ejected from the game after he gets knocked to the ground by DeMarcus Cousins and immediately bounces back up to shove him and share some choice words.

videos.headline: Morris ejected after altercation with Boogie

videos.description: The Lakers defense forces a turnover and Alex Caruso makes a nifty pass to Talen Horton-Tucker for the ferocious dunk to cap the fast break.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Horton-Tucker throws down fast-break slam) 2021/01/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Horton-Tucker throws down fast-break slam

videos.description: Talen Horton-Tucker swipes the ball away for a steal then goes coast-to-coast to spin in a tough layup off the backboard for an and-1 bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Horton-Tucker turns steal into sweet layup on the break) 2021/01/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Horton-Tucker turns steal into sweet layup on the break
